{"tid":1832981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後想知道自己放低左未嘅就入黎我話你知啦","createTime":"2020-01-21T14:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T03:26:30.000Z","uid":320831,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5b9b7db55dd026d615f5d2e8fcd1077966c6bc","tid":1832981,"uid":320831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"放低左嘅話，就唔會成日沉淪係感情台，見到個類似標題就㩒入去睇下同自己個case有咩相似地方，俾自己機會去諗返起狠心dum低你嘅嗰個人<br />\n<br />\n收手啦巴絲們，適當圍爐有幫助，但成個身心都擺晒係上面只會令你更加困住自己<br />\n<br />\n我知道你好叻，可以走到出去，但心入面可能覺得自己唔應該就咁走左去，好似如果連自己都走左就代表段感情真係好虛無咁，無存在過<br />\n<br />\n唔洗隔硬逼自己，順住個心去行，去做自己想做嘅野，唔好認為喊好懦弱，叫春好撚on9好撚廢，仼何情緒都有存在嘅意義，慢慢行落去，終有一日你會離開捆綁住你嘅嗰個循環<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝你有日唔需要再留連係感情台，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803780d93f0340617d5f5478ef8020c77e2d3530","tid":1832981,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\"></span>"},{"pid":"9e5f49b853f0a50ede331d44d0c0b4c051469a1b","tid":1832981,"uid":182134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb932b0fb557c006aaa11568052306cd0262460","tid":1832981,"uid":182134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"不過有時入黎係想睇下人間疾苦<br />\n安慰下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31e3bd726b851caa7d7febd73458e1f703e669a","tid":1832981,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"對、希望大家一齊走出去、仲有其他感情等緊大家、親情友情"},{"pid":"0db2b0a10f1448e3dc7a5e169390af811b8a2f6c","tid":1832981,"uid":134563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma